> Mitigation
> ==========
>
> Do not offer TLS for incomming connections (tls_advertise_hosts).
> This mitigation is *not* recommended!

This should block the most popular attack vector:

In your MAIL ACL:

    deny    condition = ${if eq{\\}{${substr{-1}{1}{$tls_in_sni}}}}
            message = sorry


